-- Towers of Hanoi (9 disks) -- durability proof, not computation.
-- Pre-computed 511 moves. Agent just closes steps. Proves crash-recovery at scale.

## towers-of-hanoi-9

  input param.source_peg : str default("A")
  input param.target_peg : str default("C")
  input param.auxiliary_peg : str default("B")

  # setup : text
    user>
      Verify initial state: all 9 disks stacked on peg {{param.source_peg}}.
      Largest on bottom.
    accept>
      Initial state verified.
  #/

  # move-1 : text
    - setup
    user>
      Move disk 1: A -> C
  #/

